item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

[quote=“Philosophica, post:3, topic:32264”]Personally, I use an edited version of Project 16 edit 6 v7/8 for all my server bases…try it out, but be warned: it’s a little more complex than TestScape etc.

~Philo[/quote]

Lol you said that wrong “Project 16 version 6 edit 7/8”, but that is ok ;). Anyways, wolf was going “his-own-way” for while until he released version 6, which is more based on Cheezscape like Testscape. So now P16 can be edited easily and it is still the least bugged server source available to download and the best for pking.
